description: Number of partitions satisfying (cn(0,5) = 0 and cn(1,5) <= cn(2,5) and cn(1,5) <= cn(3,5) and cn(4,5) <= cn(2,5) and cn(4,5) <= cn(3,5)).
comments: For a given partition cn(i,n) means the number of its parts equal to i modulo n.Short: (0 := 0 and 1<=2 and 1<=3 and 4<=2 and 4<=3).
